    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a HTTP response header field called Safe, which can be used to indicate that repeating a HTTP request is safe.  Such an indication will allow user agents to handle retries of some safe requests, in particular safe POST requests, in a more user-friendly way.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
